      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the mirror-finish exterior, underscores a legacy of uncompromising care. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned category, offering a showroom-quality experience for the sophisticated driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
