    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a collector-grade example that has been maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one, and all interior electronics operate with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented history of dealership-only maintenance performed ahead of schedule. It has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. The undercarriage remains spotless, and the matching set of premium tires has less than 1,000 miles of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, turn-key masterpiece for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
